ipicotool is a tool for working with RP2040/RP2350 binaries, and interacting
with RP2040/RP2350 devices when they are in BOOTSEL mode. (As of version 1.1 of
picotool it is also possible to interact with devices that are not in BOOTSEL
mode, but are using USB stdio support from the Raspberry Pi Pico SDK by using
the -f argument of picotool).
